<plot>Reanimating the horror anthology for the 21st century, HORRORSHOW unleashes five short tales of brutality, hilarity, terror and titillation to delight the darkest side of your soul: Neon Killer - as two grizzled detectives face the twilight of their careers, the identity of the sadistic maniac who has eluded them for decades is revealed; The Flea - a psychotic would-be vampire hunter tries to coax his erstwhile partner back into the fold for one last slaying; Smile - a young woman discovers that a harsh breakup can leave a lasting impression. ; The Initiation - a trip far outside the city limits leads a young couple to a place where arcane rituals have replaced all reason.; The Incursion - an intruder turns up more than he bargained for in a house full of dark secrets.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245827</url></doc>
